      "firm_id": "standard_0",
      "description": "Fair overall condition. Runs and drives, but shows noticeable wear from age and use. Expect cosmetic blemishes, interior wear, and some deferred maintenance or sorting items. A usable driver, but not a clean or fully sorted example.",
      "price": 19900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "fair",
      "quality_value": 0.4,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "Exceptional mint-condition example that presents exactly the way serious buyers hope to find one. The exterior shows beautifully with excellent paint, body, and trim, and the interior is equally well-kept with minimal to no visible wear. It runs and drives the way a properly cared-for car should, with no notable needs expected for a turn-key buyer. This is not just a usable driver but a truly standout, highly presentable car that should satisfy someone looking for a top-tier example.",
      "price": 46900.0,
      "reputation": 1.0,
      "quality": "mint",
      "quality_value": 1.0,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Reliable transportation at an accessible price, this vehicle offers solid everyday utility for the buyer who values function and affordability. It shows its age and is best suited for someone seeking a practical commuter, a first car, or a cost-effective project with real upside. Presented with straightforward value and priced to move, this is an opportunity to get into a vehicle without stretching your budget.",
      "price": 6950.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Looking for an affordable car with solid potential? This one isn\u2019t perfect, but it\u2019s a straightforward budget-friendly option for someone who wants basic transportation, a project, or a handy extra vehicle. It shows its age and needs a bit of TLC, but that\u2019s reflected in the price. If you\u2019re after something cheap, honest, and worth a look, this could be a great fit.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Solid project car with strong enthusiast potential. Advertised in poor condition, but it still offers a stout drivetrain foundation, responsive steering feel, and a chassis that\u2019s worth saving for the right buyer. Engine turns over and the car presents as a great platform for a budget build, track-prep project, or parts donor. Cosmetic wear, age-related issues, and deferred maintenance are present, so come expecting a fixer, but the fundamentals make this one compelling for someone who knows their way around a toolbox. Priced to move and ideal for an enthusiast looking for a rewarding turnaround opportunity.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Runs. Drives. Cheap way into a car now. Sold as-is in poor condition, but it gets the job done. Priced to move fast.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Here\u2019s a car with real underdog charm\u2014the kind of machine that still turns heads from people who appreciate potential over polish. It has the honest, well-lived character of a driver that\u2019s seen stories, and it\u2019s ready for someone with vision to bring it into its next chapter. Whether you want a budget runaround, a hands-on project, or a platform to make your own, this one offers a lot of personality for the money. If you enjoy the satisfaction of rescuing something with soul, this is the kind of find that makes the journey worthwhile.",
      "price": 4900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "Affordable and straightforward, this vehicle offers a practical low-cost entry point for a buyer who values budget over perfection. Best suited for someone looking for basic transportation, a project, or an economical backup vehicle, it presents a chance to own at a very approachable price. Offered transparently and priced to reflect its condition, this is a smart value opportunity for the right buyer.",
      "price": 5495.0,
      "reputation": 0.9,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Honest little car that\u2019s ready for someone who wants affordable wheels or a simple project. It\u2019s not perfect and shows its age, but it still has plenty of potential for the right buyer. Great option if you need a cheap runaround, something to tinker with, or a practical spare. Priced fairly and presented straight \u2014 come have a look and see if it\u2019s the right fit for you.",
      "price": 5900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 15
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Solid project or budget driver with strong old-school character. Engine starts, runs, and pulls with the kind of mechanical honesty enthusiasts appreciate, and the chassis feels like a good foundation for someone who wants a usable car without paying show-car money. Cosmetic wear and age are present throughout, but that\u2019s reflected in the price. A great candidate for a hands-on owner looking for affordable entry, parts support, and room to improve while enjoying it as-is.",
      "price": 6900.0,
      "reputation": 0.5,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
